text: Gilbert Dubier (14 September 1931 - 10 April 2019) was a French wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2019 deaths Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nantes
